data.title: Roger Daltrey and his band in San Diego
data.meta_description: Roger Daltrey, lead singer and founder of legendary band The Who will be at the Rady Shell at Jacobs Park, San Diego, CA on 6 May 2024 for a one-off night of solo songs, rare cuts and some Who favourites. […]
data.text:
Roger Daltrey, lead singer and founder of legendary band The Who will be at the Rady Shell at Jacobs Park, San Diego, CA on 6 May 2024 for a one-off night of solo songs, rare cuts and some Who favourites.

Roger’s band will consist of Simon Townshend, guitars; Jon Button, bass; Loren Gold, keyboards; Frank Simes, guitars; Scott Devours, drums and Katie Jacoby, violin.

Roger’s special guest for this momentous night will be the fabulous KT Tunstall.

Venue pre-sale 10.00am PT, Thursday 22 February and general on-sale 10.00am PT, Friday 23 February 2024.
